HEADWORD: Kydde
<hw>Kyd"de</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <def><pos>imp.</pos> of <er>Kythe</er>,
to show.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ Spenser erroneously uses <xex>kydst</xex> to mean
